000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-=
bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"=
>enforcement action</a> <em>against Theorem Fund Services </em>=E2=80=9Cfor=
 missing red flags=E2=80=9D; TFS settled by paying about $122,000, and real=
ly if you are a fund administrator you are kind of in the business of certi=
fying that a hedge fund is real and not a Ponzi, so this is bad.</p><p styl=
e=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The SEC charged EIA and its owner with <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32321698.266412/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
