eecd1" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background=
-color: #ccc;"> running a Ponzi</a> last year. He is far from the first per=
son to allegedly=C2=A0fall into a Ponzi scheme by losing money and thinking=
 =E2=80=9Cwell I just won=E2=80=99t tell anyone I lost money, and I=E2=80=
=99ll trade extra hard next month to make it all back.=E2=80=9D He might be=
 the first person to record that plan=C2=A0as an asset on his fund=E2=80=99=
