=E2=80=9Cholding the bag=E2=80=9D.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">The idea is that Icahn Enterprises is more or less a hedge fund in the=
 form of a public company; you can calculate the net asset value of its hol=
