=80=9D Hindenburg said on the X platform Friday. =E2=80=9CToday, $IEP repor=
ted further investment losses and slashed its dividend by 50%. We remain sh=
ort.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Roughly speaking=
